What are the benefits of picking RoR for developing web applications?
</button>
</div>
<div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
<div class="card-body">
<ul class="bullet-list">
<li>RoR is perfect for web development.</li>
<li>It's user-friendly and well-structured to overcome the difficulties in updates or deployment.</li>
<li>RoR holds some perfect testing features that collaboratively use the BDD and TDD strategies.</li>
<li>It holds gem libraries and offers rich resources for the developers to implement the features in the web app. </li>
</ul>
</div>
